## `buildLayoutClass()` Helper

Used by `set_layout`. Handles direction, align, justify, and width classes. Gap is handled separately — it writes `gap-[Npx]` to `props.className` (not `style.gap`) and the class-stripping + `style.gap` removal happen in the `set_layout` executor after `buildLayoutClass` returns. The function itself is left unaware of gap to keep it generic.
